али Ela de Longespée, 27. Он женился на женщине по имени Maud DeAudley около 1275 г. в местности эджмонд, шропшир, Англия, Великобритания. У них была по крайней мере 1 дочь. Он умер 23 ноября 1273 г. в его родном городе в возрасте 23 лет."},"sm":{"1250–23 November 1273":"1250–23 Novema 1273","1249–1317":"1249–1317","1250–1273":"1250–1273","1251–1276":"1251–1276","1251–1282":"1251–1282","1258–1299":"1258–1299","1267–1326":"1267–1326","1255–1312":"1255–1312","1257–1296":"1257–1296","1220–1272":"1220–1272","1224–1299":"1224–1299","1220":"1220","1296":"1296","1251":"1251","1273":"1273","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","1282":"1282","1326":"1326","1249":"1249","1259":"1259","1258":"1258","1257":"1257","1224":"1224","1312":"1312","1267":"1267","1255":"1255","1299":"1299","1276":"1276","11 June 1272":"11 Iuni 1272","23 November 1273":"23 Novema 1273","1317":"1317","Ireland":"Aialani","Audley, Staffordshire, England":"Audley, Staffordshire, Egelani","Audley, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Audley, Staffordshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Heighley, Staffordshire, England":"Heighley, Staffordshire, Egelani, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"1250–23 November 1273":"1250–23. november 1273","1249–1317":"1249–1317","1250–1273":"1250–1273","1251–1276":"1251–1276","1251–1282":"1251–1282","1258–1299":"1258–1299","1267–1326":"1267–1326","1255–1312":"1255–1312","1257–1296":"1257–1296","1220–1272":"1220–1272","1224–1299":"1224–1299","1220":"1220","1296":"1296","1251":"1251","1273":"1273","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","1282":"1282","1326":"1326","1249":"1249","1259":"1259","1258":"1258","1257":"1257","1224":"1224","1312":"1312","1267":"1267","1255":"1255","1299":"1299","1276":"1276","11 June 1272":"11. jún 1272","23 November 1273":"23. november 1273","1317":"1317","Ireland":"Írsko","Audley, Staffordshire, England":"Audley, Staffordshire, England","Audley, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Audley, Staffordshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Heighley, Staffordshire, England":"Heighley, S